app: 飞企互联-FE企业运营管理平台
seo: 飞企互联,FE企业运营管理平台,任意文件上传,漏洞检测
seo_en: Flychery,FE Enterprise Operation Management Platform,Arbitrary File Upload,Vulnerability Detection
summary: 该插件用于检测飞企互联-FE企业运营管理平台的officeserver模块是否存在任意文件上传漏洞，通过发送特定请求并检查响应来确认漏洞是否存在。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the officeserver module of Flychery-FE Enterprise Operation Management Platform has an arbitrary file upload vulnerability, and confirms the existence of the vulnerability by sending specific requests and checking the response.
